divs: Sighting DetailsI was going to store looked up in sky seen very bright orange light heading my direction watched as it appears to seem like airplane till it moved abruptly then went strait it seemed to brighten then started to flicker then light went out could still see object traveling in same direction I have seen meteorites in past and this wasn't one of them
Summary: Flew at slow speed in semis strait path brightens then turns invisible but can still be seen traveling at slow Speed heading north east not a asteroid
